text: Im Dong-hyun (born 12 May 1986) is a South Korean archer. Dong-hyun competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics, 2008 Summer Olympics, and the 2012 Summer Olympics.Im Dong-Hyeon ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean archers Category:Olympic gold medalists for South Korea Category:Olympic silver medalists for South Korea
